<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        border-top-left-radius: 8px;
        border-top-right-radius: 8px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        border-left: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }
      .alert-box {
        background-color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .security-tip {
        background-color: #f0f9ff;
        border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Account Locked</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @resource.name || @resource.email %>!</h2>
      
      <p>
        Your Playground account has been temporarily locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign-in attempts.
      </p>
      
      <div class="alert-box">
        <p><strong>Account Security:</strong> This is a protective measure to prevent unauthorized access to your account.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>
        To unlock your account, please click the button below:
      </p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <%= link_to 'Unlock My Account', unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token), style: 'display: inline-block; background-color: #4f46e5; color: white !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold;' %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="security-tip">
        <p><strong>Security Tip:</strong> If you're having trouble remembering your password, you can reset it after unlocking your account.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>
        If you did not attempt to sign in to your account multiple times, please contact our support team immediately at <a href="mailto:support@flukebase.me" style="color: #4f46e5;">support@flukebase.me</a> as your account may have been targeted.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The Flukebase Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Flukebase. All rights reserved.<br>
        This email was sent to <%= @resource.email %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
